               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; name of the protagonist; name of the commissioner and of her family members; groups of lines on the incipit page of Texts I; incipits of all sections of Text I and incipit of Text II; the word sälam "salutation" in Text II; elements of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals.</rubric>
                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
                  <!--The data in the items below refers to other items. please remove this items and move the information to the appropriate place.-->
