                     <note>I-2) Homily: fols. 9rb-11vb, 40ra-41vb; miracle: fols. 41vb, 13ra-vb,12ra-rb</note>
                     <note>I-3) Homily: fols. 12vb, 14ra-15vb, 17ra-18vb, 32ra-35vb, 19ra; miracle: fols. 19ra-vb, 16ra-rb</note>
                     <note>I-4) Homily: fols. 16vb, 20ra-26rb</note>
                     <note>I-5) Homily: fols. 27vb, 36ra-37vb, 28ra-31vb, 38ra; commemorative notice: fols. 38vb-39vb, 42ra.</note>
                  </msItem>
